{"tid":789983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"厭惡特朗普「作為」 克林頓女兒考慮未來從政","createTime":"2018-08-22T15:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T10:22:04.000Z","uid":60545,"like":8,"dislike":327,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"339c7734abdceafadc52dfe1aa843f0890b2d403","tid":789983,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180821/large/1534826272_b5ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180821%2Flarge%2F1534826272_b5ef.jpg&h=b0d42b9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國前總統克林頓的千金翠露絲（Chelsea Clinton）出席活動時表示，「厭惡」特朗普當總統後的作為，又斥他將偷渡父母與孩子分開拘留是「目前最大的過失」，她不排除將來從政，但現時未有實質計劃。<br />\n<br />\n翠露絲表示：「我每天都因總統而憤怒，包括他的一言一行，以及他選擇不去處理或忽視的行動，又或他在Twitter或電視上欺凌別人。」她強烈譴責特朗普對非法入境者實施的「零容忍」政策，將偷渡父母與孩子分開拘留，「我厭惡特朗普的所為，我非常感謝有女議員和參議員努力嘗試阻止他」。<br />\n<br />\n她亦指，自己不同意總統的意見，但可以參與不同角色：「對我來說，肯定現在不會(從政)，但未來肯定有可能，因為沒有人知道未來會怎樣。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/10793140/realtime/article/20180822/58588788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F10793140%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180822%2F58588788&d=wVF4sxI16Ui%2FQc7GR08yLZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=22115aac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F10793140%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180822%2F58588788&h=2c0786f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/10793140/realtime/article/20180822/58588788</a>"},{"pid":"5089670eb3a619344daeb38b470d1ecd4ad08fe9","tid":789983,"uid":94828,"like":117,"dislike":0,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:53:46.000Z","msg":"佢老豆應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4b629f66e0a9cb3798056baef6329e8e7c84a4","tid":789983,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />